FBIS3-21683 "jptdd009__l94081" JPRS-TDD-94-009-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 28 February 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Man Arrested at Oshoek Border Post With 100,000 Mandrax Tablets MB1902110094 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in English 0900 GMT 19 Feb 94 MB1902110094 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] The police have arrested a man at the Oshoek border post between South Africa and Swaziland with 100,000 mandrax tablets in his possession. The tablets, with an estimated street value of 2.5 million rands were found in his car. The man will appear in the Carolina magistrate court soon.
